title: Will David Dobrik's Dispo App Succeed or Fail? | Creator Economics #16
description: Reed and Blake discuss David Dobrik's decision to launch his own social platform, Dispo. Will this app become the next Instagram? Listen to Reed and Blake as they share their thoughts on the app and what it means for the future of Creator led companies.
dc:creator: Reed Duchscher and Blake Robbins
